Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:21.83,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,A, kỳ thiệt đó...{Ugh, this isn't right...}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:24.76,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Không làm được.{I can't. I can't do it.}
