Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:27.33,SignI,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Yết Cơ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.33,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Yết Cơ của Anija...{anjia's kirishihime is...}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:31.74,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Giờ thì còn bị vướng hơn nữa.{Now it's even more caught.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.68,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Mồ hổng chịu đâu.{I've had it with this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:37.25,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Mình muốn về nhà!{I want to go home!}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:38.27,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Để tớ thử xem.{Let me see it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:39.26,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Ể?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:45.10,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,N-Nhưng Anija bảo chỉ có người trong tộc mới được chạm vào Yết Cơ{\fscx300}-{B-But Anija said no one outside our \Nfamily can touch Kishihime—}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.41,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Sao chả được. Tránh ra.{That doesn't matter. Just give me room.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:49.44,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:03.25,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Xong rồi.{It's fixed.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:07.49,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:09.02,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Đường bị đóng băng nên trơn lắm,{The ground is frozen and slippery,}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:10.33,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,đừng leo lên đó.{so don't ride it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:11.61,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Dắt bộ về đi.{Push it home.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:13.90,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Ừ. C-Cảm{\fscx300}-{Yeah. Th-Tha—}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:18.31,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Nghe đây! Ta có lời khen ngợi ngươi hỡi đứa con của phàm nhân.{Hear me! I commend you, son of man.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:22.39,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Cô nên thôi cái kiểu nói đó đi.{You know, you should really stop that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:23.82,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Ể?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:25.20,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Cô chưa biết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:27.60,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Họ gọi những người như cô "bệnh hoang tưởng".{They call people like you "chuunibyou."}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:30.48,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Suy nghĩ cô dựng lên,{The settings you made up}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:34.61,Default - flashback,,0,0,0,,và thế giới hư cấu cô mơ ước là không có thật.{and the fictional worlds you \Nadmire don't actually exist.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:37.36,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Có ngày cô sẽ hối hận đấy,{Someday, you're likely to regret it}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:40.60,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,rồi tự hỏi:"sao mình lại nói\N mấy lời xấu hổ thế chứ?"{and wonder, "Did I really do \Nsomething that embarrassing?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:42.12,Default - flashback,,0,0,0,,Vậy nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.36,0:01:48.75,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Climax Blade White!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:48.75,SignA,Screen,0,0,0,,Bạch Thập Nhị {\c&H8A4F13&}Dực Kiếm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:57.20,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Gì vậy bà nội?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:59.66,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Im đi! Đồ ngốc!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:00.46,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:03.18,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Ngốc! Ngốc! Ngốc! Ngốc!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:05.04,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Đừng nói lời vô nghĩa nưa!{Quit spouting nonsense!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:07.27,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Hư cấu có tồn tạn!{Fiction definitely exists!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:09.24,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Sao lại có thể?{How can it exist?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:11.02,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Là hư cấu vì nó chả có ở đâu cả.{It's fiction because it doesn't exist anywhere.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.52,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Có mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.39,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Có cái vẹo.{It doesn't.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:14.49,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Có mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:15.11,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:15.73,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Có!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:16.76,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Không là không!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:18.08,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Có là có!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:20.04,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Vậy nói cho tôi biết...{Then tell me...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.34,Default - flashback,Andou,0,0,0,,Hư cấu đó ở đâu?{Where is this fiction, exactly?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:24.41,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.52,Default - flashback,Tomoyo,0,0,0,,Hư cấu có ở đây!
